{"tid":1799936,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"軍政府林總統斥示威者到商場破壞「和理非」吶喊助威難辭其咎","createTime":"2019-12-27T10:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T11:03:18.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef5749744f88f732cab64f81915563ccf78a31c","tid":1799936,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:37:15.000Z","msg":"香港警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉向會員發信表示，有示威者在一連幾日的聖誕佳節到多個商場進行破壞，認為理性的人都會感到怒髮衝冠，部分人更攻擊警務人員，彷彿要將警員置諸死地，協會對此予以最嚴厲譴責。<br />\n<br />\n林志偉說，自稱和平、理性及非暴力的人亦難辭其咎，他們在示威者的破壞過程中吶喊助威、協助逃避警察追捕，認為冷血程度配不上和平及理性。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，有組織指控警隊在聖誕前夕針對和平購物人士及示威者使用武力，他批評「被自殺」及「被性侵」等是無稽空洞的指控，毫無政治道德可言。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499835-20191227.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499835-20191227.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHco9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=6cd9b453\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499835-20191227.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=765bf389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499835-20191227.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講來講去都係果幾篤屁，就快好似耿爽咁有生成器<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af105f953f952d5d0ec653928920ba54d7ff500","tid":1799936,"uid":265839,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:38:25.000Z","msg":"他批評「被自殺」及「被性侵」等是無稽空洞的指控<br />\n<br />\n此地無銀"},{"pid":"785d0138c36ad31eb6b93af3ad224d8582929ac3","tid":1799936,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:40:28.000Z","msg":"大家幫手宣傳下，ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同你身邊既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sa5sWmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSa5sWmr.jpg&h=2e6a418c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\